    <description># ![Application Icon for Edit](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/microsoft/edit@e8d40f6e7a95a6e19765ff19621cf0d39708f7b0/assets/edit.svg) Edit

A simple editor for simple needs.

This editor pays homage to the classic [MS-DOS Editor](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MS-DOS_Editor), but with a modern interface and input controls similar to VS Code. The goal is to provide an accessible editor that even users largely unfamiliar with terminals can easily use.

![Screenshot of Edit with the About dialog in the foreground](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/microsoft/edit@bd992237010380cd24b7763ae95a23391190966a/assets/edit_hero_image.png)
